item.title: Help
item.dc:creator: @austinsobes austinsobes
item.description:
@austinsobes wrote:

ctash18:

Hello everyone. My name is cameron and i am new to rsps coding. I need help with a few things and i was wondering if anyone whith teaveiwer would be willing to help me. If so let me know. Thanks!

ollie123:

No I’m afraid we are not a spoonfeeding community. There are several good tutorials in the Server Tutorials section.

You should first start by learning was RSPS development is. Playing and developing your own RSPS are two different things. The only real advice anybody is going to give is what I’m going to say right here… Right now…

L2Program.
Grab a Java 2 learner’s book for beginners and learn what java programming is. And then once you feel comfortable with what computer programming is, and you feel comfortable in Java. Grab a source. Grab a client. And start hacking at code.
